      "text": "1. requirements\n2. core entities\n3. API / interface\n4. high level design\n5. deep dives",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. requirements\n2. core entities\n3. API / interface\n4. high level design\n5. deep dives",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "iXrIA60fq4OPCtqQku21g",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2614.6575175337553,
      "y": -80.81533089648514,
      "width": 1437.598876953125,
      "height": 425,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 341709728,
      "version": 2108,
      "versionNonce": 576777824,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "0rwRhzj3FeYVBXmT6Ib1v",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1771497410437,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "functional reqs:\n- lots of incoming events, we want to be able to count the occurences of all of them & provide a leaderboard of the k most popular events\n(number of google search terms, top spotify songs) => happens very frequently and are updated on alot of servers\n- need to re-calliberate this search over arbitrary time\n- billions of events per day k < 1000\n\nnon functional reqs:\n- 1 min between when the event happens & when it is tabulated in our top-k; [latency (write side) => things r out of order in scale]\n- 10s of ms to retrieve top-k [latency (read side)]\n    challenge: cardinality of the system: have billions of unique items => cant just sort them fast (unlike sorting 5 unique items)\n    => require pre computation\n- Billions of videos (TBD) => helps to visualize storage (sharding / replicas) => \n- hundreds of thousands of views per second (TBD) => helps to visualize write volume (QPS) => in the end was 700_000 views/s [alot of writes]\n- precise? or approx? => chosen precise results (no approximation)\n    => getting precise results is easier than a well designed approximation system\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "functional reqs:\n- lots of incoming events, we want to be able to count the occurences of all of them & provide a leaderboard of the k most popular events\n(number of google search terms, top spotify songs) => happens very frequently and are updated on alot of servers\n- need to re-calliberate this search over arbitrary time\n- billions of events per day k < 1000\n\nnon functional reqs:\n- 1 min between when the event happens & when it is tabulated in our top-k; [latency (write side) => things r out of order in scale]\n- 10s of ms to retrieve top-k [latency (read side)]\n    challenge: cardinality of the system: have billions of unique items => cant just sort them fast (unlike sorting 5 unique items)\n    => require pre computation\n- Billions of videos (TBD) => helps to visualize storage (sharding / replicas) => \n- hundreds of thousands of views per second (TBD) => helps to visualize write volume (QPS) => in the end was 700_000 views/s [alot of writes]\n- precise? or approx? => chosen precise results (no approximation)\n    => getting precise results is easier than a well designed approximation system\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "jS2DuJiw9n67vmvcjvP-l",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2336.7988958231094,
      "y": -427.76142301735695,
      "width": 705.53955078125,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a9",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1593170848,
      "version": 394,
      "versionNonce": 1727157152,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1771499813876,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "top K systems have alot of ambiguity\n- top-k most viewed videos\n- time window?\n    all time most viewed videos => not going to change alot\n    over the last week/month/day/hour => adds complexity + ambiguity\n    (sliding window vs tumbling window) => use simpler , tumbling windows!\n   ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "top K systems have alot of ambiguity\n- top-k most viewed videos\n- time window?\n    all time most viewed videos => not going to change alot\n    over the last week/month/day/hour => adds complexity + ambiguity\n    (sliding window vs tumbling window) => use simpler , tumbling windows!\n   ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
